<paragraph id="BE9CC693E7F33DEA90F8621F147FCD17" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">22.348, 103.775, 1948 m, subtropical forest, fungusy wood, beating, 23.VI.2017, R. Schuh (1 male, 1 female, CNC).</paragraph>
